Name: Lawn Aerator Roller Scarifier  Rolling Steel Spike Tool Garden Yard Farm Grass
Description:
DESCRIPTIONPlant a healthy growth, promote a beautiful lawn with our Lawn Aerator. An essential product for every garden lover, a unique design that helps strengthen the grassroots by plugging the ground with tiny holes to allow the air to better reach the roots. A simple yet effective process that will ensure your lawn stays prosperous and greener all the time.

For most lawns, the fertile soil may be buried underneath a blanket of dust, impure soil, and many more. These impurities deteriorate plant life thus tampering with delicacy. Bypass all these troubles by using our lawn aerator. It comprises of small spikes that you can roll around simultaneously to create miniature vents to offer a smoother flow of water, fertilizers, and air into the ground. It will improve the soil water absorption capacity, makes the roots strong, reduces soil compaction, and enhances thatch breakdown.

It is made of high-quality galvanized steel and PP plastic. The entire structure is built strong and tough to withstand regular and long-term usage. Its steel construction provides high resistance towards rust and corrosion, so no more worry if the conditions are wet. Very lightweight and portable, easy for you to grab and start rolling. It comes with an ergonomic long handle for improved efficiency and usability. If you want to store it – it’s simple, disassemble it into 3 pieces for easy storage.

Help the nature way, build your green way. Start lawing! Order your lawn aerator now.   

Key Features:

  • 27Galvanized spikes
  • Acerate up to 3.5cm depth
  • Lightweight and portable
  • Applicable on dirt, sand and clay
  • Improves turf health
  • Reduces thatch build-up
  • Relieves soil compaction
  • 3Pcs detachable tubular handle

SPECIFICATION

  • Spike and frame material: Galvanized steel
  • Wheel material: PP plastic
  • Diameter: 14.5 cm
  • Spike length: 3.5 cm
  • Number of spike：27
  • Weight：3.4kg
  • Dimension: 44cm x 14.5cm x 150cm
  • Colour: Green

PACKAGE CONTENTS

  • 1 x Lawn Aerator Roller
  • 1 x Instruction Manual

DESCRIPTION

Want to decorate your environments? Our Artificial Grass would be your prime choice, suitable for both indoor and outdoor environment. Name: 50PCS Synthetic Artificial Grass Turf Pins U Fastening Lawn Tent Pegs Weed Mat
Description:
DESCRIPTION

Make your synthetic grass stay firm and steady with our Grass Pins. There are numerous traditional ways to fix the synthetic grass on the ground, but these solutions have proven to be a temporary fix rather than a permanent fix. They might easily get affected due to environmental effects, for example using adhesive duct tape, it might fix the grass but with time the adhesive will wear out. Neutralize all these scenarios with our grass pins. Wondering how to use it? Simply align it with the synthetic grass and carefully punch it with a hammer or any pressure applying tool. Once punched down in the ground it perfectly disguises with the grass due to its natural green colour. No irregular surface, very soft to touch. Keeps your synthetic layer of grass firm and steady. Gives your green space a subtle look. Provides you peace of mind as displaced grass can cause a lot of trouble. A perfect addition to your precious green floor.

In terms of its quality, it is made from high tensile steel with powder coating. Highly durable and strong grass pins. It can easily withstand high pressure. Does not bend or deform due to accidental application of force. Built with unique U-shaped design makes the process of installing much easier and faster. It is not easily affected by environmental effects such as rusting due to its steel construction. It is a seamless integration of quality and appearance.   

An elegant grass floor to maintain, the extraordinary performance it provides. A smart way, a green way.

Key Features:

  • U-shape pin
  • Sturdy construction
  • High tensile steel
  • Powder coated finish
  • Corrosion resistant
  • Simple installation
SPECIFICATION

Material: Steel
Finish: Powder coated
Dimension: 150mm x 30mm x 3mm
Colour: Green
